{"tid":2098784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［中國先知共賞］［舊文］鐵道部：2020年春運緊張狀態將不復存在--時政--人民網","createTime":"2020-07-07T17:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T18:05:33.000Z","uid":203783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f275f1c2fc15d01c9e555692c98442ec42526449","tid":2098784,"uid":203783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>2008年02月20日03:37</strong>  來源：中國新聞社<br />\n<br />\n        中國鐵道部新聞發言人王勇平今天在此間表示，春運是一個歷史現象，它不會永無休止地持續下去。到二0二0年，發達完善的鐵路網將全面建成，加之其它交通運輸行業的同步發展，中國春運這一緊張狀態將不復存在。<br />\n<br />\n...........<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3iLLYjl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3iLLYjl&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=c281a7f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3iLLYjl</a><br />\n<br />\n即使推理過程出咗問題，結果仍然正確，不愧係黨<br />\n<br />\n呢位王勇平領導就係著名phrase「<span style=\"color: orange;\">反正我信了</span>」嘅出處<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbac3a0bf2946a7047686cf4e377ce0869e4d985","tid":2098784,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T18:05:33.000Z","msg":"樓主寫得幾好笑喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}